nodes.text: A rescue on Florrum was attempted by the Jedi younglings Byph, Ganodi, Gungi, Katooni, Petro, and Zatt of their mentor Ahsoka Tano, who had been captured by Hondo Ohnaka and his pirates.

Joining Preigo's Traveling World of Wonder, they infiltrated Ohnaka's camp and successfully retrieved her. However, when they returned to the Crucible, it was shot down by a WLO-5 battle tank and Ahsoka and the younglings were recaptured.
